From: Adam Scott <adamscott200322@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Jul 2026 08:32:52 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Lower vector integer division and remainder through float
 division

---
 llvm/lib/Target/X86/X86ISelLowering.cpp       | 210 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../lib/Target/X86/X86TargetTransformInfo.cpp | 120 +++++++++-
 2 files changed, 324 insertions(+), 6 deletions(-)

